However, what makes his position unusual is that now he wants to be <RP Category='HEAD_OF_STATE_TAG'><HR>President</HR></RP> and become our <RP Category='HEAD_OF_STATE_TAG'><HR>Commander in Chief</HR></RP>. 

Therefore, the big question is this: How could Bill Clinton as <RP Category='HEAD_OF_STATE_TAG'><HR>President</HR></RP> justify sending young men to war, for any reason, when he did everything possible not to go himself?
